{"tid":2019054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Fox News：美國擬對世衛恢復部分資助","createTime":"2020-05-16T04:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T04:30:24.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"373c30e4c0066db3e06a4a9e7199b22cdaaa5a15","tid":2019054,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"（中央社紐約15日綜合外電報導）美國福斯新聞頻道（Fox News）今天晚間引據一封信件草稿報導，美國總統川普政府準備要對世界衛生組織恢復部分資助。<br />\n<br />\n福斯新聞引述這封致世衛秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）的信件內容報導，川普政府將「同意在分攤費用方面和中國出的錢一樣多」。<br />\n<br />\n川普4月14日暫停美國對世衛的資助，指控世衛就2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）一事幫中國宣傳「不實訊息」，還說美國政府將對世衛展開調查。世衛官員否認這項指控，中國也堅稱對疫情一向公開透明。<br />\n<br />\n美國原是世衛最大資助國，以往每年約資助4億美元。福斯新聞報導，若美國資助金額和中國相同，新的資助金額大約是往年規模的1/10。（譯者：李佩珊/核稿：盧映孜）1090516<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202005160060.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202005160060.aspx&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=5f38d73b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202005160060.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/media/exclusive-white-house-set-restore-partial-who-funding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fexclusive-white-house-set-restore-partial-who-funding&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=01336735\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fexclusive-white-house-set-restore-partial-who-funding&h=971e77f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/media/exclusive-white-house-set-restore-partial-who-funding</a>"},{"pid":"429d80675bc312a0ba9f1354309c1681778e7d50","tid":2019054,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"[全民twitter]twitter娛樂交流區,港豬要娛樂入手<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ftPwRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ftPwRS</a>"}]}